## Description {#details}

Hierarchical <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/regionnode">RegionNode</a> successor iterator.

This iterator iterates over all successors of a <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/regionnode">RegionNode</a>.

For a <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/basicblock">BasicBlock</a> <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/regionnode">RegionNode</a> it skips all BasicBlocks that are not part of the parent <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/region">Region</a>. Furthermore for BasicBlocks that start a subregion, a <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/regionnode">RegionNode</a> representing the subregion is returned.

For a subregion <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/regionnode">RegionNode</a> there is just one successor. The <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/regionnode">RegionNode</a> representing the exit of the subregion.
